{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Martin Bokša Blog","author":"Martin Bokša"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9d8df735-5f25-5890-8361-c36d827cb7b3","excerpt":"Za posledný môj rok som sa stretol s množstvom knižníc, ktoré sa týkajú Reactu.\nJe to dané najmä tým, že som nemal veľké predchádzajúce skúsenosti s Reactom\na…","html":"<p>Za posledný môj rok som sa stretol s množstvom knižníc, ktoré sa týkajú Reactu.\nJe to dané najmä tým, že som nemal veľké predchádzajúce skúsenosti s Reactom\na zároveň javascript je tak rýchly jazyk, že vychádzá v ňom každý deň\nnové množstvo knižníc.\nRád by som si tu odložil skúsenosti s nimi a priblížil vám čo všetko považujem\ndnes za nevynutné vedieť pri práci s Reactom.</p>\n<h2>Boilerplate</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app\">create-react-app</a>\nak nemáte skúsenosti s Reactom, táto knižnica vám vytvorí boilerplate (alebo kostru) pre vašu\naplikáciu. Obsahuje všetky nevyhnuté konfigurácie a závislosti aby ste mohli\nrovno písať React a nemuseli sa o nič starať.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"no-text\"><pre class=\"language-no-text\"><code class=\"language-no-text\">What&#39;s included? React, JSX, ES6, TypeScript and Flow syntax support.</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Data Store</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/reduxjs/react-redux\">Redux</a> ide o globálny obchod s premennými. Je vhodný k tomu,\naby ste nemuseli preposielať premennú cez ďalších <em>x</em> komponent do hĺbky. Tak ju\nnapojíte na globálne obchod. Použitie napríklad: user data, aktuálna téma, stav aplikácie, …\nPoužíva sa často.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 38.24091778202677%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Redux\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/1a291/redux.png 148w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/2bc4a/redux.png 295w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png 590w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/526de/redux.png 885w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fa2eb/redux.png 1180w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png 1569w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/context.html\">React Context</a> je to pomerne nová feature od Reactu.\nJe teoretickým nahraditeľom Reduxu. Tu sa, ale vytvorí <code class=\"language-text\">provider</code> dát a\njeho vnútorné komponenty vo vnútri ich vedia čitať pomocou <code class=\"language-text\">consumera</code>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/c312a/react-context.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.42253521126761%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"React Context\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/fb8a0/react-context.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/1a291/react-context.png 148w,\n/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/2bc4a/react-context.png 295w,\n/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/fb8a0/react-context.png 590w,\n/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/c312a/react-context.png 710w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mobxjs/mobx\">MobX</a> ďalšia možnosť k uskladneniu\nglobálnych dát.</p>\n<h2>Serverová komunikácia</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\">fetch</a> natívny príkaz z ES6,\nktorým je možné dopytovať server. Funguje pomocou <strong>Promise</strong>, ale chýbajú mu zatiaľ\nnejaké funkcie ako napríklad <strong>abort</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/axios/axios\">Axios</a> rozšírená verzia <strong>fetch</strong>, založená tiež\nna <strong>Promise</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> axios <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'axios'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\naxios\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'/user?ID=12345'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>response<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>response<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/apollographql/apollo-client\">Apollo Client</a> knižnica s plnou podporou\npre <a href=\"https://graphql.org/\">GraphQL</a>. Ponúka tiež <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/apollo-client-developer-t/jdkknkkbebbapilgoeccciglkfbmbnfm\">dev tools</a> pre Chrome.\nOdporúčam pri používaní Reactu si pozrieť GrapQL. Namiesto reťazových volaní na server, je\nmožné ich nahradiť za jeden.</p>\n<h2>CSS</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/styled-components/styled-components\">Styled Component</a> vizualizácia\nkomponentov v javascripte pomocou CSS. Výhodou je napríklad vynutie sa class-name konfliktov.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber 0\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Button <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>a<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n  display: inline-block;\n  color: #e62076;\n`</span></span>\n<span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Button href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.martinboksa.eu/\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>GitHub<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Button<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Material UI\n<a href=\"https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui\">https://github.com/mui-org/material-ui</a></p>\n<p>classnames\n<a href=\"https://github.com/JedWatson/classnames\">https://github.com/JedWatson/classnames</a></p>\n<p>react-responsive\n<a href=\"https://github.com/contra/react-responsive\">https://github.com/contra/react-responsive</a></p>\n<p>React DnD\n<a href=\"https://github.com/react-dnd/react-dnd\">https://github.com/react-dnd/react-dnd</a></p>\n<p>React Spring\n<a href=\"https://github.com/react-spring/react-spring\">https://github.com/react-spring/react-spring</a></p>\n<p>React Bootstrap\n<a href=\"https://github.com/react-bootstrap/react-bootstrap\">https://github.com/react-bootstrap/react-bootstrap</a></p>\n<h2>Internationalization</h2>\n<p>react-i18next\n<a href=\"https://github.com/i18next/react-i18next\">https://github.com/i18next/react-i18next</a></p>\n<h2>Testing</h2>\n<p>Jest\n<a href=\"https://jestjs.io/en/\">https://jestjs.io/en/</a></p>\n<p>Test Utilities\n<a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/test-utils.html\">https://reactjs.org/docs/test-utils.html</a></p>\n<p>Enzyme\n<a href=\"https://github.com/airbnb/enzyme\">https://github.com/airbnb/enzyme</a></p>\n<h1>Meta Tags</h1>\n<p>React Helmet\n<a href=\"https://github.com/nfl/react-helmet\">https://github.com/nfl/react-helmet</a></p>\n<h1>Forms</h1>\n<p>Redux Form</p>\n<h1>Utils</h1>\n<p>lodash\nmomentjs</p>\n<h1>Rich Editor</h1>\n<p>Draft.js\n<a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/draft-js\">https://github.com/facebook/draft-js</a></p>\n<h1>Type Checking</h1>\n<p>PropTypes\n<a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/typechecking-with-proptypes.html\">https://reactjs.org/docs/typechecking-with-proptypes.html</a></p>\n<p>flow\n<a href=\"https://flow.org/en/docs/frameworks/react/\">https://flow.org/en/docs/frameworks/react/</a></p>\n<p>TypeScript\n<a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/\">https://www.typescriptlang.org/</a></p>\n<h2>Nice to know</h2>\n<p>StoryBook\nprettier\neslint</p>\n<h2>Package Manager</h2>\n<p>npm\nyarn</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Necessary React libraries and skills!","date":"January 06, 2019"},"timeToRead":3}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/necessary-react-libraries/","previous":null,"next":null}}